{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/YouAreRoot.png?t=1728823603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/You_are_Root_gif_3.gif?t=1728823603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A sophisticated <strong>malware</strong> created with a sole objective: bypass the defenses of malfunctioning computer systems by <strong>erasing</strong> their cyberspace, in order to reset them to their default state and bring them back to life again. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Now it's time for you to take on a <strong>new job</strong>, in a <strong>new system</strong>. Nothing more than just the same old <strong>routine</strong>... probably. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/Trial_Error.png?t=1728823603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/Trial_and_Error_gif_1.gif?t=1728823603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies are <strong>fragile</strong> and can be erased in <strong>one single hit</strong>, but <strong>so are you</strong>, malware; you must <strong>wipe out</strong> every single defences in an area, in order to proceed to the next one. If you fail, iterate and <strong>try again</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/Abilities.png?t=1728823603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/Combat_Gif_3.gif?t=1728823603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are equipped with various <strong>abilities</strong> (or functions, if you prefer); a good malware knows how to use <strong>each tool</strong> at its disposal, to be as <strong>efficient</strong> as possible during <strong>combat</strong>. Jump, dodge attacks, deflect bullets, throw your trusty scythe. Do everything in your power to <strong>complete your tasks</strong>.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"P-Test_Simulation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2557480/b34179bdaabe87c3c6881115a9c6c7a5bf656bae.jpg"},{"name":"Same Old Routine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2557480/b34179bdaabe87c3c6881115a9c6c7a5bf656bae.jpg"},{"name":"Root_0.1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2557480/b34179bdaabe87c3c6881115a9c6c7a5bf656bae.jpg"},{"name":"Root_0.5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2557480/b34179bdaabe87c3c6881115a9c6c7a5bf656bae.jpg"},{"name":"Root_1.0","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2557480/b34179bdaabe87c3c6881115a9c6c7a5bf656bae.jpg"},{"name":"Infect and Erase","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2557480/b34179bdaabe87c3c6881115a9c6c7a5bf656bae.jpg"},{"name":"Security Breach","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2557480/b34179bdaabe87c3c6881115a9c6c7a5bf656bae.jpg"},{"name":"Network-fall","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2557480/b34179bdaabe87c3c6881115a9c6c7a5bf656bae.jpg"},{"name":"Surprise Cyber-attack","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2557480/b34179bdaabe87c3c6881115a9c6c7a5bf656bae.jpg"},{"name":"Friendly fire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2557480/b34179bdaabe87c3c6881115a9c6c7a5bf656bae.jpg"}],"total":30},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/a